### Search HTTP tests

@base=http://localhost:8000
@json=application/json
@token=YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Search all
GET {{base}}/api/search?q=document
Accept: {{json}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search files only
GET {{base}}/api/search/files?q=pdf
Accept: {{json}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search folders only
GET {{base}}/api/search/folders?q=project
Accept: {{json}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get search suggestions
GET {{base}}/api/search/suggestions?q=doc
Accept: {{json}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

